            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and mix well – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage</strong></p>",
